def naca(m, p, t, x):
    yt = 5.0*t*(0.2969*sp.sqrt(x) -0.1037*x*x*x*x + 0.2843*x*x*x - 0.3516*x*x - 0.126*x)
    
    yc = sp.Piecewise(
    (m/p**2 * (2*p*x-x**2), x <= p),
    ((m/(1-p)**2)*((1-2*p)+2*p*x-x**2), True)
    )
    
    dycdx = sp.diff(yc, x).simplify()
            
    omega = sp.atan(dycdx)
    
    xU = x - yt * sp.sin(omega)
    xL = x + yt * sp.sin(omega)
    yU = yc + yt * sp.cos(omega)
    yL = yc - yt * sp.cos(omega)
    
    return [xU, yU, xL, yL, yc]

def naca_abs(m, p, t, x):
    yt = sp.Function('yt')(x,t)
    ycL = sp.Function('ycL')(m,p,x)
    ycG = sp.Function('ycG')(m,p,x)
    
    yc = sp.Piecewise(
    (ycL, x <= p),
    (ycG, True)
    )
    
    dycdx = sp.diff(yc, x).simplify()
            
    omega = sp.atan(dycdx)
    
    xU = x - yt * sp.sin(omega)
    xL = x + yt * sp.sin(omega)
    yU = yc + yt * sp.cos(omega)
    yL = yc - yt * sp.cos(omega)
    
    return [xU, yU, xL, yL, yc]
